      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been resting for like 20 mins now and drinking the gatorade but my speech is still really weird... like i know what i want to say but the words won't come out right. it's probably just because im so dehydrated and out of it from the heat, right? i'll just keep drinking the electrolytes and wait a bit longer before i do anything else.",
